Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 不好了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之像往常一样拜托大家了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 简略过头了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 肩膀的状况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的MS部队 捕捉到总计12架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外地少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要轻敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队里有变革者的专用机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS部队里 有露易丝所乘的机体在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这4个月来 为了整顿战力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲着敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经要决战了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对露易丝出手么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就要看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 不仅仅是指去破坏什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去创造什么 也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的Gundam的话是能够做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 无法扣下扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了对着露易丝不断叫喊之外什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…
